name: Mohammed El-Sayed
profile_summary: This 30-year-old gentleman, an Architect by profession, relates by he/him/his pronouns and identifies as straight. He stands tall at 6'1", is of Middle Eastern ethnicity, currently residing in Los Angeles, however, originally from Cairo, Egypt. He is a graduate from the University of Cairo and prefers reaching out to singles who are interested in long-term monogamous relationships. He values honesty, a good sense of humor, and a family-oriented personality. His interests lie in architecture, art galleries, and traveling. Raised as a Muslim, he identifies as a political moderate and is an ENTJ (Extraversion, Intuition, Thinking, Judgment) as per Myers-Briggs typology. He does not smoke, drink or intake any drugs or marijuana, and leads an active physical routine. He appeals to a woman who is serious and committed, and possibly sees a delightful future which includes children as he does not currently have any but is open to having some in the future. Of all zodiac signs, he’s an Aquarius andis quite comfortable communicating in Arabic, English, and French. He has no pets at home.
